=Description=

"ChipIn, is a web-based service that simplifies the process of collecting money from groups of people.  The ChipIn Widget is a simple application that lets you keep people up-to-date on your fundraising efforts. Start at the ChipIn website to quickly create a widget stating what you're collecting for, how much you want to raise, an end-date and how you'd like to receive your funds (credit card or Paypal). It also makes it easy to track your progress on your blog or website and invite others to contribute to your cause. Once the widget is created, you copy-paste it into your website"
(http://www.chipin.com/)


